data.description: Pride of Homeownership Shows in this Gahanna schools Condo! Walk into that white kitchen connecting to dining area to the amazing high ceiling living room. A half bath here. Shiny hardwood floor on entry level and brand new carpet upstairs & well maintained carpet in finished basement. The upstairs offers 1 master bed with master bath in it and the 2nd bed with the hall full bath. 2 car garages! There is a big green space on the side with no neighbor at the back but fenced in yard & concrete patio. Conveniently located by 270/Taylor rd/Hamilton Rd with all the stores and restaurants nearby yet in a small community with only 34 homeowners. AC only 1.5 years. Nothing to do but move in and enjoy!
